message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with sound localisation, which is a subfield of signal processing. Other likely categories could be cs.SD (Speech and Audio Processing), cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the paper uses convolutional neural networks, cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper proposes an end-to-end system approach using a neural network, and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper deals with intelligent systems for sound localisation.
